# File: app/styles/bootstrap-theme.css.ab
# Purpose: Bootstrap 3.3.7 theme CSS — unminified copy with optional visual enhancements stored in app/styles/
# Dependencies: []

## Overview
Unminified copy of the Bootstrap 3.3.7 optional theme CSS (587 lines). Adds gradient, shadow, and transition visual enhancements on top of the base Bootstrap styles, providing a slightly richer default appearance for buttons, navbars, and wells.

## Interface
No exports. Reference file; `bootstrap-theme.min.css` is the production version.

## Dependencies
No project-level dependencies. Vendor file. Requires `bootstrap.css` to be loaded first.

## Implementation Notes
- Bootstrap theme version: 3.3.7
- 587 lines unminified
- Identical in content to `app/assets/css/bootstrap-theme.css`
- Optional theme that extends base Bootstrap with additional visual styling
